  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>A continental buffet is served each morning with a selection of pastries, fruit and coffee.</p>
<p>The restaurant is fantastic and serves lots of fresh fish! The terrace has panoramic views of the lake, so it's a lovely setting for dinner. We'd recommend having dinner there during your stay (payable locally). </p>
<p>The bar's open from 9am - 11pm and you can take your drinks out onto the terrace to make the most of the views.</p>]]></cateringDescription>
