  <description><![CDATA[<p>Hotel Bellavista definitely lives up to its name. The views are incredible. It’s right on the lake edge and we love relaxing by the pool and looking out over <a data-udi="umb://document/7d421e04a79044babf8cafda30e31d4a" href="/{localLink:umb://document/7d421e04a79044babf8cafda30e31d4a}" title="Lake Como">Lake Como</a>.</p>
<h2>Time to explore?</h2>
<p>The Bellavista's a great base for an active holiday. You can spend your days out exploring the many towns and walking spots on the lake – they’re easily accessible by ferry. Speak to the hotel staff who’d be happy to recommend things to see and do. The hotel’s next to the centre of town and has a brilliant choice of shops, bars and restaurants right on its doorstep.</p>
<h2>Enjoy fresh fish in the restaurant</h2>
<p>The hotel restaurant's under different management and is renowned for its fantastic food. Head here for local delicacies and fresh fish right from the lake. The al fresco veranda is the perfect spot to enjoy dinner and an aperitivo as the sun sets behind the mountains.</p>]]></description>
