  <listingDescription><![CDATA[<p>We can't get enough of the views at the Hotel Bellavista - the best ones are from the pool where you can settle down with a good book and gaze out over <a data-udi="umb://document/7d421e04a79044babf8cafda30e31d4a" href="/{localLink:umb://document/7d421e04a79044babf8cafda30e31d4a}" title="Lake Como">Lake Como</a>. It's a great base for an active holiday. Being in the centre of Menaggio means there's lots to explore right on the doorstep and you can easily jump on a ferry to get to more lakeside towns.</p>]]></listingDescription>
