  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Lake View Rooms </strong>sleep up to two people in a double or twin beds. They have lake views from the window. They have a shower.</p>
<p><strong>Lake View Rooms with balcony </strong>sleep two guests and have a bath or shower, these are available for a supplement. </p>
<p><strong>Single Rooms</strong> are also available. These rooms have a shower and look out across <span>the road.</span></p>
<p><strong>All rooms have:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Air-conditioning</li>
<li>TV</li>
<li>Hairdryer</li>
<li>Minibar</li>
<li>Safe</li>
</ul>
<p>Cots are available on request for approx. €10 per day, payable locally.</p>
<p><strong>Local fees &amp; taxes</strong></p>
<p>A resort tax of approx. €3 per person per day (applies to stays of up to 10 days) is payable locally.</p>
<p><strong>Accessibility</strong></p>]]></roomsDescription>
